  "reference_number": "SSU0012",
  "remarks": "\nGeneral James Nando (NANDO) is an involved person under The South Sudan (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 for commanding SSPDF elements to carry out attacks in Tambura County between June and September 2021, mobilising them to use rape as a weapon of war, as well as abduct and kill civilians, loot civilian and humanitarian properties, cause forceful displacement of civilians, and use civilians, including children, as forced labour. This was done in violation of international humanitarian law. \n",
